<p>
  In contrast, market-rate apartment complexes that contain a few BMR units typically do not advertise these BMR units on their property website.  Instead, when a BMR waitlist opens for a market-rate complex, the relevant income and rent information can be found on a separate affordable housing website.  It is hard to find values for our database for these types of properties unless a waitlist opening (also called an <b>opportunity drawing</b>) exists at that moment, in which case the supplemental affordable housing website for that property can be used.  An example of one of these supplemental websites is the <a href="https://www.housekeys13.com/rental-opportunities" target="_blank">Mountain View HouseKeys</a> website.
