<h2 id="using-the-updates-tool">Using the updates tool</h2>
<p>
  Our affordable housing updates tool is used by volunteers like you to help us keep our database up-to-date.  This manual checking process supplements a separate automated system we use to scan for updates each day.  Properties that need a manual review are periodically grouped into a <b>campaign</b>.  Once onboarded, you will automatically get notified of any new campaigns we publish. Once all the properties in a given campaign have been checked, the campaign is finished!  Multiple volunteers working together helps the campaign finish faster.  And don't worry, nothing you do here will affect our live website&mdash;all submitted changes will need database admin approval before they become live!
</p>

