<h3 id="tips">Tips</h3>

<h4 id="tips-waitlist-status">Waitlist status</h4>
<p>
  Some property managers do not list the open/closed waitlist status on individual property pages.  Instead, they have a single central location with the status of all their properties.  Sometimes it's under "portfolio" or "our properties" or "find a home." Be sure to poke around the website a bit to find this information if it's not prominently displayed on the individual property page, as this is perhaps the most important piece of information.
</p>
