<h4 id="income-and-rent-data">Income and rent data</h4>
<p>
  Sometimes, properties will not show detailed occupancy, income, and rent information on the main property page.  Instead, there will be a link to <b>tenant selection criteria</b>, a <b>property flyer</b>, a <b>move-in qualification sheet</b>, or similar.  Explore all the links on a property page to (hopefully) find the details you are looking for.
</p>
