<h4 id="populations-served">Populations served</h4>
<p>
  One of the fields, <b>populations served</b>, can be a bit confusing.  The purpose of this field is to help visitors to our website find properties that <i>specifically</i> cater to their own population segment.  There are specific categories such as <b>seniors</b> or <b>developmentally disabled</b> and then there is a catch-all default category called <b>general population</b>.  Most properties will be in the general population category (sometimes also called "family housing").
</p>
